Hello, everybody!

Yet another bug has been discovered in the implementation of the SHA
that is available from our ftp site. The bug involves computing the
SHA hash when stdin is redirected. It has been fixed now, and the
fixed package is available, as usual, as

ftp.informatik.uni-hamburg.de:/pub/virus/texts/crypto/shs.zip

Thanks to the people who noticed the bug and sorry for any confusion
that has been caused by it.

Regards,
Vesselin
